mock_job_name-metadata.failure-reason: ClientError: Annotation tasks expired.  Probable Reasons are 1) TaskAvailabilityLifetimeInSeconds parameter is too small.  2) Reward is too low for workers to work on the task.  3) If you use a custom html template, your template may be broken.  4) Data (image/video/text) sent for annotation is broken or too big, preventing completion.  5) All workers declined the tasks.
